title: Coronavirus: Italy's Death Toll Exceeds 11,000, 812 Die in 24 Hours
description: In the last 24 hours, 812 people have died in Italy from the Chinese coronavirus, bringing the nation's overall death toll to 11,591 as of Monday -- an increase of 7.5 per cent in one day.
